    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>What is CyberSurfer?</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247860/extras/2c2dfd8d8137c9d3e83643c2ff2df16d.poster.avif?t=1746036439\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247860/extras/2c2dfd8d8137c9d3e83643c2ff2df16d.webm?t=1746036439\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247860/extras/2c2dfd8d8137c9d3e83643c2ff2df16d.mp4?t=1746036439\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Put down the controllers of yesterday and pick up your phone to experience an intuitive experience. Race on a hoverboard in time trials to get the best time and see who is the fastest in the world! Learn a new way to move through the universe, a new way to control your path!<br><br>In short, CyberSurfer is a desktop game with a mobile phone as the controller.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Your phone, a new controller</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247860/extras/e8437dc287190e6b6753f3f8f031a19e.poster.avif?t=1746036439\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247860/extras/e8437dc287190e6b6753f3f8f031a19e.webm?t=1746036439\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247860/extras/e8437dc287190e6b6753f3f8f031a19e.mp4?t=1746036439\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Pick up your smart phone to have an intuitive an exhilarating experience. Simply connect with the CyberSurfer app and be launched into the void.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>How do I download the Mobile App?</strong></h2>Select the Mobile App OS to download the CyberSurfer mobile app!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Customize your hoverboard</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247860/extras/4d2d7a6e19d41d409075e06d1a4749cb.poster.avif?t=1746036439\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247860/extras/4d2d7a6e19d41d409075e06d1a4749cb.webm?t=1746036439\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247860/extras/4d2d7a6e19d41d409075e06d1a4749cb.mp4?t=1746036439\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>What’s a cool way to show your cred. Show off your prized cyberboard. Race for amazing designs and hoverboards that help you in ways you never thought of.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Who is the fastest in the World?</strong></h2>Spanning over 300 years, a cybernetic racing culture defines many entities realites. Your purpose is to beat the tyranical robots no matter the cost. Play as a Human, Cyborg, or  Robot and step up to the plate. Join the race, because there’s only one way out.<br><br><br>Travel the cybernetic universe while being transported by worm holes. Master the art of flying on the CyberBoard using astronomical phenomena to benefit your movements.",
